
# Dependency

* GO >= 1.7
* bcc env

# Install guild

## Required Linux Kernel 4.4+

If you are on Ubuntu, get kernel packeage from here:
http://kernel.ubuntu.com/~kernel-ppa/mainline

## Install BCC tool set

https://github.com/iovisor/bcc/blob/master/INSTALL.md

# Roadmap

* ipsec support
* various tunnel support (gre， vti， vxlan…)
* netns support
* tcp/udp support
* reorganise the cli show output to make it more informative. 
* high performance/low overhead various counters. Target to be feasible in production environment
* packet tracing across multiple boxes
* NB apis for query & management

